
Testing of foobar2000 media player control in home-assistant
This component requires pyfoobar2k
https://bitbucket.org/ed0zer/pyfoobar2k

Setup:
place foobar.py and pyfoobar2k/ into custom_components/media_player/
follow instrunctions in pyfoobar2k to setup foobar2000

media_player:
  - platform: foobar
    host: 192.168.1.100

Additional config parameters:
media_player:
  - platform: foobar
    name: entity name
    host: 192.168.1.100
    username: username
    password: password
